reviewText:
Said check region code before purchasing. No region code given. Looked at item none on picture. Said German/English. Well I get it today and DVD falls out because case wasn't closed all way and sure enough, dvd says region 2. So I now own a dvd I can't play. Wouldn't buy again from this seller. Who am I gonna sell it to in region 1 where I live?
Not happy.
I could not play the movie on my player
As a person who is obsessed with Jane Austen I absolutely loved this set. It was super cute and I'm glad that I found it.
This DVD does not work on any DVD player. I bought it and wasted my money
